### ========================================
### AI防诈骗问答功能 - 简化测试
### ========================================

### 基础配置
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ========================================
### 0. 用户登录（获取Token）
### ========================================

### 0.1 登录获取JWT Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 登录成功后，将返回的token复制到下面
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ========================================
### 1. 创建新会话
### ========================================

### 1.1 创建新的AI对话会话
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/session
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ========================================
### 2. AI问答核心测试
### ========================================

### 2.1 识别诈骗风险 - 冒充公检法
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "question": "有人打电话说是公安局的，说我涉嫌洗钱，要我转账到安全账户，这是诈骗吗？",
  "sessionId": ""
}

###

### 2.2 识别诈骗风险 - 刷单返利
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "question": "网上有人让我刷单返利，说每单能赚50元，这是真的吗？",
  "sessionId": ""
}

###

### 2.3 识别诈骗风险 - 虚假投资
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "question": "有个投资平台说日收益10%，保本保息，可以投资吗？",
  "sessionId": ""
}

###

### 2.4 防范建议 - 如何防范电信诈骗
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "question": "如何防范电信诈骗？",
  "sessionId": ""
}

###

### 2.5 知识普及 - 什么是杀猪盘
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "question": "什么是杀猪盘诈骗？",
  "sessionId": ""
}

###

### 2.6 紧急求助 - 已经被骗了怎么办
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "question": "我已经被骗了5万元，应该怎么办？",
  "sessionId": ""
}

###

### ========================================
### 3. 多轮对话测试
### ========================================

### 3.1 第一轮对话
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "question": "什么是电信诈骗？",
  "sessionId": "test-session-001"
}

###

### 3.2 第二轮对话（基于上下文）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "question": "那具体有哪些常见的电信诈骗手段？",
  "sessionId": "test-session-001"
}

###

### 3.3 第三轮对话（基于上下文）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "question": "如果遇到这些情况，应该怎么防范？",
  "sessionId": "test-session-001"
}

###

### ========================================
### 4. 查询对话历史
### ========================================

### 4.1 获取指定会话的历史记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/history?sessionId=test-session-001&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4.2 获取用户所有对话历史
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/history?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ========================================
### 5. 清除对话历史
### ========================================

### 5.1 清除指定会话的历史
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/history?sessionId=test-session-001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5.2 清除用户所有对话历史
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
